{
  "stem": "3150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They dug a grave, made them kneel, and they shot them in the back, and they all fell in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the reason I'm-- I'm so much aware exactly how they were killed-- because there were a lot of rumors going on for months.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were working over here and working over there, because nobody wanted to believe that's what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of my distant relatives, distant uncle, he was one of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he fell in alive, and he came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the rumors that were going on for weeks-- they were working over here and working over  there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We knew, but he was in hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He couldn't come out and say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew that where-- they are four kilometers in the forest, and they're all dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Taken to work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was probably-- about that time, it was probably about a half a dozen Germans, and the rest of them were Ukraine police, which worked with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our area, where I was born, the Ukraines probably did 90% of the killing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because when they liquidated our ghetto, which later on, I believe they had, like, three Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest of them were all-- all Ukraines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, because he's supposed to be dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he-- he nobody ever saw him, really.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, except my-- my father saw him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never see him for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but while we were in hiding, you know, the farther you tell the story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody thought they're working over here and working over there, you know, all the rumors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he knew they were four kilometers away, and none of them are  alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
